    Job1USA - Full Life Cycle Recruiter / HR Generalist - Multiple Accounts
    August 2009 - May 2010 (10 months)
    Toledo, Ohio Metropolitan Area
    Responsible to effectively recruit, train, screen and maintain quality employees
